 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Phil Hilgaertner''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Mark Davis''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 1989-1992\n|\n*'''[[Whitfield Crane]]''' \u2013 lead vocals\n*'''Klaus Eichstadt''' \u2013 lead guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Roger Lahr''' \u2013 rhythm guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Cordell Crockett]]''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Mark Davis''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 1992-1993\n|\n*'''[[Whitfield Crane]]''' \u2013 lead vocals\n*'''Klaus Eichstadt''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Dave Fortman]]''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Cordell Crockett]]''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Mark Davis''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 1994\n|\n*'''[[Whitfield Crane]]''' \u2013 lead vocals\n*'''Klaus Eichstadt''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Dave Fortman]]''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Cordell Crockett]]''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''Bob Fernandez''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 1994\u20131997\n|\n*'''[[Whitfield Crane]]''' \u2013 lead vocals\n*'''Klaus Eichstadt''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Dave Fortman]]''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Cordell Crockett]]''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Shannon Larkin]]''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 1997\u20132010\n|\n'''Disbanded'''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#e7ebee;\"| 2010\u2013present\n|\n*'''[[Whitfield Crane]]''' \u2013 lead vocals\n*'''Klaus Eichstadt''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Dave Fortman]]''' \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Cordell Crockett]]''' \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Shannon Larkin]]''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n===Studio albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album details\n! colspan=\"8\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications<br><small>([[List of music recording certifications|sales thresholds]])</small>\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br><ref name=\"Billboard 200\">{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=ugly kid joe|chart=Billboard 200}}|title=Ugly Kid Joe Album & Song Chart History: Billboard 200|publisher=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6746159/ugly-kid-joe-billboard-charts-new-album|title=Ugly Kid Joe Return to Billboard Charts with New Album|website=Billboard.com|accessdate=November 26, 2019}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=a|title=australian-charts.com - Australian charts portal|publisher=Australian-charts.com|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br><ref name=\"AUT\">{{cite web|url=http://austriancharts.at/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=a|title=austriancharts.at - Austria Top 40|publisher=Austriancharts.at|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br><ref name=\"NOR\">{{cite web|url=http://norwegiancharts.com/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=a|title=norwegiancharts.com - Norwegian charts portal|publisher=Norwegiancharts.com|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand#Sales charts|NZ]]<br><ref name=\"NZ\">{{cite web|url=https://charts.nz/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=a|title=charts.nz - New Zealand charts portal|publisher=Charts.nz|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://swedishcharts.com/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=a|title=swedishcharts.com - Swedish charts portal|publisher=Swedishcharts.com|accessdate=August 20, 2010}}</ref>\n! 