ly+Kid+Joe&cat=s|title=lescharts.com - Les charts portal|publisher=Lescharts.com|accessdate=August 21, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://norwegiancharts.com/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=s|title=norwegiancharts.com - Norwegian charts portal|publisher=Norwegiancharts.com|accessdate=August 21, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand#Sales charts|NZ]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://charts.nz/search.asp?search=Ugly+Kid+Joe&cat=s|title=charts.nz - New Zealand charts portal|publisher=Charts.nz|accessdate=August 21, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://swedishcharts.com/search.asp?cat=s&search=Ugly+Kid+Joe|title=swedishcharts.org - Swedish charts portal|publisher=Swedishcharts.com|accessdate=July 23, 2012}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"Chart Stats\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1991\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"[[Everything About You (Ugly Kid Joe song)|Everything About You]]\"\n| 9\n| 6\n| \u2014\n| 4\n| 25\n| 5\n| \u2014\n| 15\n| 3\n| \n*[[Australian Recording Industry Association|AUS]]: Platinum<ref name=ryan>{{cite book|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|title=Australia's Music Charts 1988-2010|year=2011|publisher=Moonlight Publishing|location=Mt. Martha, VIC, Australia}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''As Ugly As They Wanna Be''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Madman\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014 \n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Sweet Leaf/Funky Fresh Country Club\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014 \n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 1992\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Neighbor\"\n| \u2014\n| 29\n| \u2014\n| 28\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 28\n| \n| rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''America's Least Wanted''\n