deration of the Phonographic Industry|SWI]]: Gold<ref name=\"hitparade.ch\">{{cite web|author=Steffen Hung |url=http://hitparade.ch/awards.asp?year=1993 |title=Die Offizielle Schweizer Hitparade und Music Community |website=Hitparade.ch |accessdate=October 21, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1995\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| '''''[[Menace to Sobriety (Ugly Kid Joe album)|Menace to Sobriety]]'''''\n* Released: June 1995\n* Label: Mercury Records\n| 178\n| 19\n| 24\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 22\n| 25\n| \n|-\n| 1996\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| '''''[[Motel California]]'''''\n* Released: October 22, 1996\n* Label: Evilution/Castle Records\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 128\n| \n|-\n| 2015\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| '''''[[Uglier Than They Used ta Be]]'''''\n* Released: September 18, 2015 ([[PledgeMusic|PMU]]) <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pledgemusic.com/projects/ukjrc |title=Archived copy |access-date=February 24, 2015 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150224101658/http://www.pledgemusic.com/projects/ukjrc |archive-date=February 24, 2015 }}</ref> <br> October 16, 2015 ([[North America|NA]]) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/ugly-kid-joes-uglier-than-they-used-ta-be-gets-release-date-more-details-revealed/|title=UGLY KID JOE's 'Uglier Than They Used Ta Be' Gets Release Date; More Details Revealed|date=August 18, 2015|website=Blabbermouth.net|accessdate=November 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* Label: Metalville / UKJ Records\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 84\n| \n|-\n| colspan=\"15\" style=\"font-size:8pt\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart.\n|}\n\n===Extended plays===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album details\n! colspan=\"6\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:30px;\"| US<br><ref name=\"Billboard 200\" />\n! style=\"width: