on: Genma Wars]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|\u00a51,060,000,000{{ref |JPgross|JP}} ({{nts|prefix=$|4500000}})\n|{{N/a|TBD}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>http://www.eiren.org/toukei/1983.html|title=Kako haiky\u016b sh\u016bny\u016b j\u014di sakuhin 1980-nen</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>[[List of animated feature films of 1984|1984]]</center>\n|''[[Doraemon: Nobita's Great Adventure into the Underworld]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|\u00a51,650,000,000{{ref |JPgross|JP}} ({{nts|prefix=$|13500000}})\n|{{N/a|TBD}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>http://www.generalworks.com/databank/movie/rank04.html</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>[[List of animated feature films of 1985|1985]]</center>\n|''[[The Care Bears Movie]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|34000000}} ({{nts|prefix=$|22934622}}){{ref |USgross|*}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|2000000}}\u2013{{nts|4500000}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"bears\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>[[List of animated feature films of 1986|1986]]</center>\n|''[[An American Tail]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|84542002}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|9000000}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"tail\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>[[List of animated feature films of 1987|1987]]</center>\n|''[[Doraemon: Nobita and the Knights on Dinosaurs]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|\u00a51,500,000,000{{ref |JPgross|JP}} ({{nts|prefix=$|9800000}})\n|{{N/a|TBD}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>http://www.generalworks.com/databank/movie/rank04.html</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>[[List of animated feature films of 1988|1988]]</center>\n|''[[Oliver and Company]]''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|{{#expr:100000000+21000000}}}}+ ({{nts|prefix=$|100000000}})+\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|{{nts|prefix=$|31000000}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite magazine|magazine=[[Daily Variety]]